  "body": "[pnpm](https://pnpm.js.org) use a different folder structure for node_modules which allows it to be more strict : package that are not direct dependencies of the project are not visible \r\n\r\nThis folder structure make buidler fails to detect typescript support. \r\n\r\nso when executing a package.json scruipt using buidler it trigger the buidler create project welcome screen as it cannot find buidler.config.js (even though buidler.config.ts is present)\r\n\r\n",
